# 📋 Requirements

## 🔧 Hardware Components

### Controllers
- ESP32-S3
- ESP32-CAM
- ESP32 DevKit

### Sensors
- Camera Module
- GPS Module
- MPU6050 (IMU)
- LiDAR Sensor
- Thermal Camera
- Ultrasonic Sensor

### Communication
- LoRa SX1278 Module

### Drone Components
- Drone Frame & Propellers
- Brushless DC Motors
- Electronic Speed Controllers (ESCs)

### Rover Components
- DC Geared Motors
- Motor Driver (L298N / TB6612FNG)

### Power System
- LiPo Battery
- Power Distribution Board (PDB)
- Voltage Regulator (BEC / DC-DC Buck Converter)

